OL,3,CChina clay mining explained as
OL,4,Cmillions invested in Cornwall
OL,6,FA mineral supplier has announced it
OL,7,Fwill invest nearly #18million in a new
OL,8,Fchina clay plant in Cornwall, which
OL,9,Fwill reduce its electricity use in the
OL,10,FDuchy by 10%.
OL,12,FImerys which has been extracting china
OL,13,Fclay (kaolin) in the county for more
OL,14,Fthan 25 years, will now build a dry
OL,15,Fmining plant near Roche - where clay
OL,16,Fwill be extracted and processed
OL,17,Fwithout significant water usage.
OL,19,FIt's hoped the facility will be up and
OL,20,Frunning by 2026.
