OL,3,CChina clay mining explained as
OL,4,Cmillions invested in Cornwall
OL,6,FThis, in short, involves removing
OL,7,Ftopsoil and rock, extracting the clay,
OL,8,Fand processing it to separate it from
OL,9,Fother materials.
OL,11,FKaolin is exported around the world
OL,12,Ffrom Cornwall for use in ceramics,
OL,13,Fpaints, coatings, plastics and life
OL,14,Fsciences.
OL,16,FMore than #2million of funding for the
OL,17,Fnew development in Cornwall is
OL,18,Fgovernment-granted, through the UK
OL,19,FShared Prosperity Fund.
OL,21,FWhat will happen to the existing plant?
