OL,3,CChina clay mining explained as
OL,4,Cmillions invested in Cornwall
OL,6,FThe relocation of the new facility
OL,7,Fwill also mean that the existing plant
OL,8,Fis decommissioned, creating access to
OL,9,Fadditional kaolin reserves and
OL,10,Fextending the life of kaolin
OL,11,Foperations in Cornwall.
OL,13,FMark Hewson, who leads Imerys in the
OL,14,FUK said: "We have been active here for
OL,15,Fover 25 years, with China clay, or
OL,16,Fkaolin as it's also known - being
OL,17,Fmined here for nearly 300 years.
