OL,3,CChina clay mining explained as
OL,4,Cmillions invested in Cornwall
OL,6,F"Lithium mining here in the South West
OL,7,Fis strategically important for the UK
OL,8,Fas we move forward to net zero, but in
OL,9,Fparallel to that - kaolin mining has
OL,10,Fbeen and will continue to be a
OL,11,Fmainstay of the Cornish economy.
OL,13,F"This investment is essential as we
OL,14,Fdevelop and improve our existing
OL,15,Fmining infrastructure - as this will
OL,16,Ffacilitate the set up of our lithium
OL,17,Fproject - which is located in an old
OL,18,FChina clay pit.
